  Test it right now:
  php scripts/email-broadcast.php \
    -s "Test Email" \
    -m "Hello from VeriBits!" \
    --test \
    --test-email "your@email.com"

  Or send the announcement to everyone:
  php scripts/email-broadcast.php \
    -s "VeriBits Enterprise Features Released" \
    -f example-announcement.txt \
    -t all
